@startuml
title URL Link Extraction V2 Flow

actor Client
participant LinksController
participant LinkLister

Client -> LinksController: HTTP request to /links-v2 with URL parameter
note right: Client requests improved link extraction

LinksController -> LinkLister: getLinksV2(url)
note right: Extract links using improved method

LinksController <-- LinkLister: List<String> (List of extracted links)
Client <-- LinksController: Return JSON response with links
note right: Send extracted links to client

alt BadRequest occurs
    LinkLister --> LinksController: Propagate BadRequest exception
    note right: Error handling for invalid requests
    
    LinksController --> Client: Spring's exception handler processes BadRequest
    note right: Spring converts exception to HTTP error response
end
@enduml